          <h3 class="kindle-pillar-title">E-Ink Display Specialists</h3>
          <p class="kindle-pillar-body">E-Ink electrophoretic displays used in Kindle e-readers are fundamentally different from standard LCD or OLED screens — they require model-specific panels and careful disassembly procedures that most general repair shops don't have experience with. We stock E-Ink replacement modules for current Kindle generations and handle the repair correctly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="kindle-pillar-card">
          <div class="kindle-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="kindle-pillar-title">Honest Repair vs Replace Advice</h3>
          <p class="kindle-pillar-body">An E-Ink screen replacement can sometimes approach the cost of a new entry-level Kindle — we'll always tell you that before starting. For Fire tablets, repair almost always makes financial sense. We give you the real numbers upfront so you can decide with full information — we'd rather give you good advice than take your money for a repair that doesn't make sense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="kindle-pillar-card">
          <div class="kindle-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="kindle-pillar-title">Same-Day Service Available</h3>
          <p class="kindle-pillar-body">Most Fire tablet battery and charging port repairs are completed same-day at our Winnipeg St. Vital location. Kindle E-Ink screen repairs may require parts ordering depending on your model — contact us to confirm availability before visiting so we can have your parts ready.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="kindle-pillar-card">
          <div class="kindle-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="kindle-pillar-title">Warranty on Every Repair</h3>
          <p class="kindle-pillar-body">Screen repairs carry a 30-day to lifetime warranty depending on part tier. Battery replacements include a 90-day warranty. All other repairs carry a lifetime warranty on parts and labour — so your device keeps working after it leaves our shop.</p>
        </div>
